"METRONOME - A Metronome program\n\n"

"Usage: METRONOME <BPM> <NOTE>\n\n"

"\tBPM\tBeats per minute\n"
"\tNOTE\tNote interval (1=whole, 2=half, 4=quarter, 8=eighth, 16=sixteenth)\n\n"

"Example:\n"
"\tMETRONOME 120 4\tQuarter note beat at 120 BPM\n"
"\tMETRONOME 120 8\tEighth note ticks\n\n"

"Press ESC to stop the metronome.\n"